I'm thrilled to announce that along with @thebrotherstrust I'll be hosting the #VentureIntoCures digital stream on November 18 for @ebresearch! The event will raise awareness and funds to find treatments and a cure for Epidermolysis Bullosa (EB), a rare and life-threatening genetic skin disorder that affects children from birth. This is a cause close to my heart, and I'm honoured to know families who battle this devastating disorder. They are true superheroes. Through the work of EB Research Partnership, a cure for EB is within reach, and you can help us get there. RSVP to watch the show on 11/18 at 8pm ET and make a donation to critical research at the link in my bio
